3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper addresses the challenge of cross-modality adaptation, which is a problem that falls under the broader umbrella of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with 3D shapes, which are commonly used in computer graphics applications.
